Name: PUNCH FIT
About the game: Punch Fit is the answer to your exercise needs. Follow the example and punch and dodge for an easy and fun workout. Learn various combinations of punches, dodges, and rushes to make your play more exhilarating and pleasant. OVER 50 WORKOUTS Enjoy a workout that suits your needs in terms of time and difficulty. We plan to add more and more new workouts in the future. EXERCISE REWARDS Exercise and earn drop points to get skin packs. You can get over 100 skins. EXCITING BACKGROUND MUSIC We have prepared a variety of background music to match your workout. Let's get into the groove and have fun. UPCOMING UPDATES Add new actions Add new workouts Add new skins New environments Manage play records and more...
